c: 2
v: 136
t: "Bathi “siyakholwa kuMvelinqangi nakulokho okwehliselwe kuthina, futhi nakulokho okwehliselwa ku-Abrahamu naku- Ishmayeli naku-Isaka nakuJakobe nasezizweni, futhi nalokho okwanikwa uMose noJesu nalokho okwanikwa abaphrofethi okuvela eNkosini yabo. Asibandlululi (umphrofethi) ngisho noyedwa phakathi kwabo futhi singabazinikele kuye (uMvelinqangi)"